Work today was so much fun, because I was so nervouse I was going to mess up and one of my supervisers stood behind me like the entire day and cracked little jokes. I had so much fun, I enjoy it so much. I got like a million people apps.
I went to see the Killers on friday and everyone told me they put on a really bad live show, but I think they put on a wonderful live show, they had amazing lighting. It was a lot of fun!
I was supposed to meet with a bunch of people to be productive this weekend, but no one answers their phones so that's that.
I really want to go see Rilo Kiley and Mates of State. I think I am going to go to the mates of state, if their is enough room in Mirandas car, but Rilo Kiley is at the Woodlands Pavilion and they are playing with Coldplay. The only time I have not been asleep today was when I was off at the doctors office(see previous post)
And now I am still tired.

I am going crazy. School is shit right now. I am trying to get my math grade caught up, and my grandma is bitching at me for not finishing my room. She says my room being clean is more important than my math grade. I also need to go in and retake my U.S history tests. Both of them. 
I need like a b in both classes. 
I do not know. 
AHHHHHH!
I want to scream.

Yesterday was really fun. Tiffany rocks my face off. Zio's is soooooooooo good. I wish I had more of their food. 
I so did not know we had a jamba juice right there, if I knew we did I would be there like all the time.
I love Jamba Juice.

School today kinda sucked. I am doing bad in two classes...that I know of. 
I was really tired and could not concentrate on anything.
I think I am going to take a nap later.

The tournament was friday and saturday. I think it went really well, there was a few minor problems, nothing we could not deal with.
Alissa and Niki make me want to throw up hearts and glitter(stolen from Danielle), because they are so awesome.
I am excited and I want to plan another tournament for like January, but I know we will not be able to, but at least we will be doing district. That is going to be kick ass!
My feet are so sore, and I did not wake up until 12:30 todaY. 
Score 1 for catching up on sleep!

I love most of my debate team!

-School.
-Thespians
-Sandwiches and milk
-Taking showers than making signs and getting marker on your hands.

-Driving with a group of people listening to music.
-Trying to be half as good as one of my best friends...but knowing I never will because she rocks at like...everything.
-Sleep

See you fucks tomorrow.

I am at the library(for those of you who did not read my last post)
And the big female security guard just yelled at this little boy to sit down...AND SHE MADE HIM CRY!
So, now all the librarians and stuff are trying to calm him down...she feels like an ass.

School was fun. I hung out with my fag posse at lunch. Man those kids rock my face. I am at the library right now waiting for like 4:45 to come so I can go to the school to work on the tournament. We are far behind on the tournament and I am freaking out, much like anyone else who cares about how the tournament goes.

More notes of the day:
-I got a 6 on the AP essay that I thought destroyed me, a 6 is a high B so I guess that is okay.
-Newspaper is going to look awesome
-Mrs. Licon was moody today.
-The tournament is so close.
-Shelby is so cool. We walked to the library together. I love the fact that we have become friends. It makes me smile.
:D   <---- Like that!
Is it weird that I got home from school...like twenty minutes ago, and am going back up to school at 6 in the morning?

Notes for the day:
*Kellen's party rocked my face
*Buxton makes me smile
*People not helping on the tournament piss me off.
*Stupid people who jump to conclusions piss me off.
*I finally finished the song I had been working on...it is called "Notice me" and I like it, I know it may need some work. But I like it. 

Have fun you fucks.

P.S Mrs. Roberts is still making me angry...what a bitch.

Okay, so the 80's dance thing was a lot of fun for me, I get a kick out of things like that, but hey that is just me. Oh well. So Louis, Sara, Ameneh, Brandon, Shahaeen and well that's it...decide that we would all stay at my house tonight, and as much as I love them, I want to go to sleep. Oh well, deal with it.

Everything is gay. Not like me gay, but like stupid gay. I hate it. For further information please direct your eyes to my most recent post, prior to this one.


Well 
I think I may go to that damn 80's thing, but I will not dress up. Oh well, deal with it!

Have you ever felt like you could go away and never return to what you have known, and you would not feel bad about it?
I do not mean like go away as in to a different state, I mean go away is in to a different form of being, a place where you wouldn't care about what used to be, or what never was. 
That is how I feel right now. Nothing is going good, and I hate it. I hate being all angsty because I really want to talk to people but I do not want to let them in on what is wrong because it is my problem, and I do not want their pity.

Nothing anyone can say or do can make this better...well maybe their is one person, but he will never feel for me like I feel for him.

You are so perfect for me, yet I am the only one who sees it. Why is that? Why is it that I know that we could be happy, but you are so oblivious. I wish you were like me, but I know you are not. I yearn to feel your lips again. That was magical.

What is this?
Why are my feelings so twisted?
Am I the only one who feels this way?
You are so popular, you are on everyone's mind.
So the thought that you would even choose me over the beauties is just, stupid.
Why do you keep me in wonderment about your feelings. Are they there, or not? Do you care or not? I need to know, it is driving me insane. We need to talk.
